latestPosts.caption:
Shravani takes us through an afternoon immersed in art, culture, and creativity, showcasing Roerich’s iconic work, especially his breathtaking depictions of the Indian Himalayas through tempera colors. 
His legacy goes beyond art — it embodies empathy, unity, and respect.

Roerich’s contributions to art, peace, and the India-Russia relationship are a powerful reminder that art transcends aesthetics.

This is an exhibition every art lover must experience! 

#ngma #ngmaart #artgallery #nicholasroerich #artbeyondcanvas #mixologist
